caption.p: Chemical composition of essential oils extracted from the aerial parts of Bupleurum scorzonerifolium Willd. from different countries or regions.

fn.p: a RI, retention indices: experimental, for our data (RI, retention index as determined on a HP-5MS column using the homologous series of n-hydrocarbons). b Percentage values are means of three determinations with an RSD% for the main components below 5% in all cases.
